    <JadeMethod name="initFromUserWindow" id="6f6aab8c-eba9-4e69-b62d-42d8af0f4f17">
        <updating/>
        <source>initFromUserWindow(_userWindow: CM_UserWindow) updating;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
28 April 2021	navndl1	Initial creation	TFS 50906

